[{"text": "Imagine, if you will -- a gift.", "start": 16.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'd like for you to picture it in your mind.", "start": 20.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's not too big --", "start": 23.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about the size of a golf ball.", "start": 25.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So envision what it looks like all wrapped up.", "start": 27.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But before I show you what's inside,", "start": 30.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I will tell you, it's going to do incredible things for you.", "start": 33.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It will bring all of your family together.", "start": 36.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You will feel loved and appreciated like never before", "start": 40.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and reconnect with friends and acquaintances", "start": 43.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you haven't heard from in years.", "start": 45.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Adoration and admiration", "start": 47.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "will overwhelm you.", "start": 49.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It will recalibrate what's most important in your life.", "start": 52.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It will redefine your sense", "start": 55.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of spirituality and faith.", "start": 57.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You'll have a new understanding", "start": 60.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and trust in your body.", "start": 62.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You'll have unsurpassed vitality and energy.", "start": 64.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You'll expand your vocabulary,", "start": 67.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "meet new people,", "start": 69.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and you'll have a healthier lifestyle.", "start": 71.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And get this --", "start": 74.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you'll have an eight-week vacation", "start": 76.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of doing absolutely nothing.", "start": 78.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You'll eat countless gourmet meals.", "start": 81.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Flowers will arrive by the truckload.", "start": 84.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "People will say to you,", "start": 87.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"You look great. Have you had any work done?\"", "start": 89.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And you'll have a lifetime supply", "start": 92.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of good drugs.", "start": 94.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You'll be challenged, inspired,", "start": 97.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "motivated and humbled.", "start": 100.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Your life will have new meaning.", "start": 103.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Peace, health,", "start": 106.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "serenity, happiness,", "start": 108.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "nirvana.", "start": 111.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The price?", "start": 113.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "$55,000,", "start": 115.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and that's an incredible deal.", "start": 118.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "By now I know you're dying to know", "start": 121.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "what it is and where you can get one.", "start": 123.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Does Amazon carry it?", "start": 126.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Does it have the Apple logo on it?", "start": 128.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Is there a waiting list?", "start": 130.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Not likely.", "start": 133.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This gift came to me about five months ago.", "start": 135.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It looked more like this when it was all wrapped up --", "start": 138.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not quite so pretty.", "start": 140.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And this,", "start": 143.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and then this.", "start": 146.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It was a rare gem --", "start": 149.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a brain tumor,", "start": 151.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "hemangioblastoma --", "start": 153.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the gift that keeps on giving.", "start": 156.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And while I'm okay now,", "start": 159.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I wouldn't wish this gift for you.", "start": 161.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I'm not sure you'd want it.", "start": 163.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But I wouldn't change my experience.", "start": 165.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It profoundly altered my life", "start": 168.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in ways I didn't expect", "start": 171.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in all the ways I just shared with you.", "start": 173.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So the next time you're faced", "start": 175.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with something that's unexpected,", "start": 177.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "unwanted and uncertain,", "start": 180.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "consider", "start": 183.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that it just may be a gift.", "start": 185.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 188.26, "duration": 3.0}]